Scons: Move the creation of base_env into a function

As with the earlier refactoring, this will make it easier to
instantiate envs twice, for x86-32 and x86-64.  It is also cleaner to
move code out of the Python top level.

The help text and COVERAGE_TARGETS can move to pre_base_env since they
are not trusted-env-specific.

